articles.title: Yemen’s Houthis ‘will not stop’ Red Sea attacks until Israel ends Gaza war - Al Jazeera English
articles.description: US launches maritime coalition to counter attacks the rebel group says are a response to Israeli ‘crimes’ in Gaza Strip.
articles.content: Yemens Houthis will not halt attacks on ships linked to Israel in the Red Sea, despite the United States announcing a new maritime protection force to counter them, a spokesperson for the rebel group… [+4167 chars]
